webpackJsonp([88469289332646],{8850:function(e,t){e.exports={pathContext:{group:[{node:{fields:{title:"Twenty Percent",date:"21 May 2003",slug:"/2003-05-21-twenty-percent/",tags:"Y2003"},html:'<p>At work, it looks like things might be coming together for <a href="http://www.papascott.de/2003/05/08/2214.php">reduced hours</a> starting June 1. The proposal for our department is an across-the-board 20% reduction. That means we can work 4 day weeks, or work 2 half-days and 3 full-days or whatever. The state (un)employment office will cover 60% of lost wages for 6 months. That\'s a solution that\'s fair and that I can live with, although I don\'t really have any confidence that things will be better in 6 months, either with my present employer or the job market in general.</p>\n<p>Meanwhile, my new <a href="http://www.nokia.com/nokia/0,,2273,00.html">Nokia 3650</a> cell phone arrived last night, and Mama had what she called \'car pornography\' (brochures for the <a href="http://www.bmw.de/de/produkte/automobiles/index2.html?model=5series">new BMW 5 series</a>), so we each had our entertainment last night after Christopher was asleep.</p>'},next:{fields:{title:"The Bird Goes to Work",date:"21 May 2003",slug:"/2003-05-21-the-bird-goes-to-work/"}},previous:{fields:{title:"Does this thing work?",date:"22 May 2003",slug:"/2003-05-22-does-this-thing-work/"}}},{node:{fields:{title:"The Bird Goes to Work",date:"21 May 2003",slug:"/2003-05-21-the-bird-goes-to-work/",tags:"Y2003"},html:'<p><a title="Knock \'em dead, Shelley!" href="http://weblog.burningbird.net/fires/001226.htm">The Bird goes to work</a></p>'},next:{fields:{title:"Faux Pax Americana",date:"21 May 2003",slug:"/2003-05-21-faux-pax-americana/"}},previous:{fields:{title:"Twenty Percent",date:"21 May 2003",slug:"/2003-05-21-twenty-percent/"}}},{node:{fields:{title:"Faux Pax Americana",date:"21 May 2003",slug:"/2003-05-21-faux-pax-americana/",tags:"Y2003"},html:'<p><a title="Plenty of troops to win the war, not nearly enough to win the peace" href="http://www.washingtonmonthly.com/features/2003/0306.carter.html">Faux Pax Americana</a></p>'},next:{fields:{title:"Et tu, Bavaria?",date:"21 May 2003",slug:"/2003-05-21-et-tu-bavaria/"}},previous:{fields:{title:"The Bird Goes to Work",date:"21 May 2003",slug:"/2003-05-21-the-bird-goes-to-work/"}}}],pathPrefix:"",first:!1,last:!1,index:729,pageCount:1101}}}});
